"title": "2560: Jesus Christ, resurrection of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2560: jesus christ, resurrection of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>True Christian preaching is centred on the fact that God raised Jesus Christ from the dead so that believers may have victory over sin and death and receive the blessings of eternal life.</p>\n<h2>The resurrection of Jesus Christ is foretold</h2>\n<h3>In Scripture</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:3-1Cor15:4\">1CO 15:3–15:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:10\">PSA 16:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:15\">PSA 49:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:10-Isa53:12\">ISA 53:10–53:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:2\">HOS 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:46\">LUK 24:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:29-Acts2:31\">ACT 2:29–2:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:22-Acts26:23\">ACT 26:22–26:23</a></p>\n<h3>By Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:21\">MAT 16:21</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:31\">MRK 8:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:22\">LUK 9:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:40\">MAT 12:40</a> <em>the sign of Jonah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:9\">MAT 17:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:9\">MRK 9:9</a> <em>the transfiguration</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:22-Matt17:23\">MAT 17:22–17:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:31\">MRK 9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:18-Matt20:19\">MAT 20:18–20:19</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:33-Mark10:34\">MRK 10:33–10:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:31-Luke18:33\">LUK 18:31–18:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:32\">MAT 26:32</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:28\">MRK 14:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:19-John2:22\">JHN 2:19–2:22</a> <em>Jesus Christ clears the temple</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:16\">JHN 16:16</a></p>\n<h2>The resurrection is preached by the apostles</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:33\">ACT 4:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:24-Acts2:32\">ACT 2:24–2:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:40-Acts10:41\">ACT 10:40–10:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:2-Acts17:3\">ACT 17:2–17:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:18\">ACT 17:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">ACT 17:31</a></p>\n<h2>The certainty of the resurrection</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:3\">ACT 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:3-1Cor15:8\">1CO 15:3–15:8</a>LUK <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor24:36-1Cor24:43\">24:36–24:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:26-John20:28\">JHN 20:26–20:28</a></p>\n<h2>The necessity of the resurrection</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:17\">1CO 15:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:9\">JHN 20:9</a></p>\n<h2>The results of Jesus Christ's resurrection</h2>\n<h3>God's power is demonstrated</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:19-Eph1:20\">EPH 1:19–1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:24\">ACT 2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:14\">1CO 6:14</a></p>\n<h3>The sonship of Jesus Christ is declared</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:4\">ROM 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:33\">ACT 13:33</a></p>\n<h3>The lordship of Jesus Christ is declared</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:9\">ROM 14:9</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:30-Acts5:31\">ACT 5:30–5:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:20-Eph1:22\">EPH 1:20–1:22</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:15\">2CO 5:15</a></p>\n<h3>The destruction of death's power is declared</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:18\">REV 1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:24\">ACT 2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:9\">ROM 6:9</a></p>\n<h2>The benefits of Jesus Christ's resurrection for believers</h2>\n<h3>It is the foundation of salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:25\">ROM 4:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:25-John11:26\">JHN 11:25–11:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:9\">ROM 10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:21\">1PE 1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:21\">1PE 3:21</a></p>\n<h3>It provides the power to live for God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:4\">ROM 6:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:4\">ROM 7:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:11\">ROM 8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:7\">EPH 2:4–2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:8-Phil3:11\">PHP 3:8–3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:12\">COL 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:1\">COL 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:20-Heb13:21\">HEB 13:20–13:21</a></p>\n<h3>The intercession of Jesus Christ depends upon it</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:34\">ROM 8:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:25\">HEB 7:25</a></p>\n<h3>It brings assurance of resurrection to eternal life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:14\">1CO 6:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:5\">ROM 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:20-1Cor15:22\">1CO 15:20–15:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:14\">2CO 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:14\">1TH 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:4\">1PE 1:3–1:4</a></p>",
